<section class="about-intro">
  <h1>I'm Aisha, a Brooklyn native now based in Montpellier.</h1>
  <p>Born and raised in Brooklyn, I've spent the last decade living across Paris, Amsterdam, and now Montpellier.</p>
  <p>I've always loved the overlap between design and science. And, as an INFJ who cares deeply about the people I design for and the people I work with, UX design and research became a natural fit.</p>
  <p>For the last 15 years, I've focused on turning tricky product challenges into experiences people enjoy and trust. Previously Lead Designer at Skillcrush and Senior UX Designer and team lead at Booking.com.</p>
  <p>Since 2021, I've worked as a consultant for companies and organizations of all sizes to strengthen and improve customer experiences. I help teams deeply understand their users through research, then tackle complex problems strategically and iteratively, always with collaboration at the center.</p>
</section>

